    I bought this Aquaphor lip repair because my lips get painfully dry, especially in colder weather, and it worked better than regular lip balms. It goes on smooth, feels soothing right away, and actually lasts instead of disappearing in minutes. After a couple days of use, the cracking was gone and my lips felt soft again. The tubes are small but convenient, and having two is perfect for keeping one at home and one in my bag. If you struggle with chronically dry lips, this is one of the few products that truly helps.

